★★★★★ FOR MORE ALTERNATIVE VIEWS TV: https://archive.org/details/alternative_views ★★★★★
Alternative Views #064: WILLIAM KUNSTLER: SPEAKS ON JUSTICE IN AMERICA The noted civil rights lawyer talks about the attacks on our civil liberties; past FBI abuses; Senate Bill 1 and its progeny; the decisions of the Supreme Court,; and the move in Congress to unleash the FBI and CIA. Many of the Church Committee findings are discussed.

For more related content, please visit: https://archive.org/details/@altviewstv-fanclub
